Colorful clouds at sunset, behind the Togetsu Bridge in Arashiyama. Shot on Fujichrome Velvia100 film.
</p>

<p class="jp">
嵐山の渡月橋の夕暮れ時の色とりどりの雲。Fujichrome Velvia100 フィルムで撮影。
 </p>]]></content><author><name>Daniel Sofer</name></author><category term="Arashiyama" /><category term="Togetsu Bridge" /><category term="Sunset" /><category term="Film" /><summary type="html"><![CDATA[Colorful clouds at sunset, behind the Togetsu Bridge in Arashiyama. Shot on Fujichrome Velvia100 film.]]></summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2024/2410_A7R06159_ai.jpg" /><media:content medium="image" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2024/2410_A7R06159_ai.jpg" xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" /></entry><entry><title type="html">Along the Katsura River・桂川沿い</title><link href="https://hermosawavephotography.com/240925/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Along the Katsura River・桂川沿い" /><published>2024-09-25T00:00:00+09:00</published><updated>2024-09-25T00:00:00+09:00</updated><id>https://hermosawavephotography.com/katsura</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://hermosawavephotography.com/240925/"><![CDATA[<p class="en">
Looking south towards Matsuo Taisha, along the Katsura River in Arashiyama.
</p>

<p class="jp">
嵐山の桂川沿いから南に松尾大社方面を望む。
 </p>]]></content><author><name>Daniel Sofer</name></author><category term="Arashiyama" /><category term="Katsura River" /><summary type="html"><![CDATA[Looking south towards Matsuo Taisha, along the Katsura River in Arashiyama.]]></summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2024/2409_IMG_0317-2.jpg" /><media:content medium="image" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2024/2409_IMG_0317-2.jpg" xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" /></entry><entry><title type="html">Shinjuku Highrises・新宿の高層ビル群</title><link href="https://hermosawavephotography.com/240924/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Shinjuku Highrises・新宿の高層ビル群" /><published>2024-09-24T00:00:00+09:00</published><updated>2024-09-24T00:00:00+09:00</updated><id>https://hermosawavephotography.com/shinjuku</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://hermosawavephotography.com/240924/"><![CDATA[<p class="en">
